Opposition

Decision

The complainants filed this complaint on 25.3.2003 against the opposite party to the effect that the opposite department had drawn the name of complainant No. 1 for the LIG First colony situated in Bung-8, Kanpur on the basis of lottery.
One line missed
D.530, D.430 to Complainant No. 4, C.64 to Complainant No. 5
C.336 to Complainant No. 6, and C.127 to Complainant No. 7
LIG were allotted. Installments for which were being paid.
The complainants were demanding the defendant to register the said buildings.

